<title>ʿny qḍy̱</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿny qḍy̱ rby ạlḥnwn wdẖạq gẖṣạt ạlmnwn
 mḥrraⁿạ ạ̉sry̱ ạlsjwn rb ạlwry̱ fạdy ạlậnạm
 ạlqrạr- jỷt sẖfạʾ mt fdạʾ fyạlḥbk ạlʿjyb
 lys swạk wbdmạk njwt mn mwt rhyb fkyf ạ̉nsy̱
 sẖạfy jrwḥy mạḥy ạ̉tẖạmy fkyf ạ̉nsy̱
 lwlạk ạ̉nt ḥby wʿwny rby ạ̉nt fy ạlḥsẖạ fln ạ̉nsạk
 2- kyf qḍy̱ yạllʿjb fwq ṣlyb mn kẖsẖb
 bạlṣlb qd mḥy̱ ạlgẖḍb wṣyt ṣlḥ wslạm
 3- sạlt ynạbyʿ dmạh ḥbaⁿ̃ạ ḥnạnaⁿạ llkẖṭạh
 mạ mn rjạʾ bswạh ywly ạlkẖlạṣ bạltmạm</lyrics>
